txt.en: The bundle of supplies you brought to Gwingris has concerned Daegennan greatly.

'With one delivery lost and the worms on the rise, we have need of your help.

'It is unlikely that all of the delivery is completely lost. If you find any more goods from this delivery, please bring them back to me.

'I believe that you will find more of the supplies along the road from Rivendell, well to the east.'
Daegennan believes that more of the lost supplies may be found along the path from Rivendell, well to the east of Gwingris.\n\nDaegennan has asked you to recover more of the missing supplies.
'Thank you, [placeholder]. Thank you, indeed!\n\n'These supplies should hold us until we can arrange for another delivery from Rivendell.'
'These supplies will go long way towards keeping us through the winter.'
'Be sure to keep an eye out for any crates or satchels that match the one you brought us.\n\n'They would likely be down in the valley east of Gwingris.'
Bring the recovered supplies to Daegennan
